title: City of Greater Sudbury Fire Services Receives Donated Pet Oxygen Masks (City of Greater Sudbury) ...
text: ( Source : City of Greater Sudbury ) City of Greater Sudbury's fire crews now have 8 more pet oxygen masks that can be used on any domestic animal that needs help breathing due to smoke inhalation. The donation was part of a national effort
